    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驶入<strong>《Cosmic Royale》</strong>的赛场，感受融入星际元素的巅峰对决。39 位车手逐鹿星轨，运筹帷幄，在极速淘汰赛中争夺至高荣耀。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与好友畅玩</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多邀请 <strong>3</strong> 位好友加入小队，但要记住，胜利者只能有一个。愿最佳者胜出！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精彩游戏模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>障碍赛</strong>：跨越一系列极具挑战性的障碍，在时间耗尽前抵达终点线！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存模式</strong>：加入紧张激烈的快节奏求生比赛，存活时间最长的人就是赢家！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>绝命模式</strong>：一念生死，极限挑战容不得半点闪失！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/564f68af99171a2ec70ca95d81969936.poster.avif?t=1764348993\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/564f68af99171a2ec70ca95d81969936.webm?t=1764348993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/564f68af99171a2ec70ca95d81969936.mp4?t=1764348993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发挥创造力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浏览海量选择，打造属于自己的个性卡丁车和车手。获取 <strong>Cosmic Pass</strong>，解锁专属外观、车手、战旗等特殊内容。炫出自己独一无二的风格，在一众玩家中脱颖而出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/04119dc4f59463f9c2e65ea114844f99.poster.avif?t=1764348993\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/04119dc4f59463f9c2e65ea114844f99.webm?t=1764348993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315830/extras/04119dc4f59463f9c2e65ea114844f99.mp4?t=1764348993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速进阶辅助</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集卡丁车，升级卡丁车视觉效果，提升 <strong>Rewardator</strong> 倍率。倍率越高，Cosmic Pass 推进速度越快，独占内容解锁速度也将随之飙升！</p>",
